strings:
<voice_0x01000AA2><se_high>Jessica: I don't have time to argue!
I want you to put out to sea NOW!

<voice_0x01000AA3><se_low>*: My apologies, Miss Jessica, but the waters
are simply too dangerous at the moment...

<voice_0x01000AA4><se_high>Jessica: Haven't you been listening?
I TOLD you I'd take care of that!

<voice_0x01000AA5><se_low>*: Please forgive me, Lady Jessica!
There'd be hell to pay from the Albert family
if we put you in danger!
<voice_0x01000AA6><se_high>Jessica: Is there ANYONE around here with half a brain!?
<voice_0x01000AA7><se_high>Jessica: Ah! Speak of the devil!

<voice_0x01000AA8><se_high>Jessica: You're the travellers from the tower!
Didn't I tell you to wait for me in Alexandria!?

<voice_0x01000AA9><se_high>Jessica: I wanted to properly apologise to you!
Well, whatever. I'm glad you're here now.

<voice_0x01000AAA><se_high>Jessica: Actually, I have a favour to ask.
Would you mind coming over here for a minute?

<voice_0x01000AAB><se_high>Jessica: So you're saying you won't let me fight the
sea monster?
<voice_0x01000AAC><se_low>*: Well, yes, but... Well I mean...
<voice_0x01000AAD><se_high>Jessica: Fine, fine. Not to worry. I've asked these sturdy men to take care of it for me. Okay?
<voice_0x01000AAE><se_low>*: Er... Oh, well... Actually, we've been looking for someone to take on that very job ourselves!

<voice_0x01000AAF><se_high>Jessica: Well, there you have it.
Everyone's happy.
Can I count on you guys?

<voice_0x01000AC6><se_high>Jessica: You need to prepare some things first?
Then don't just stand around, get on with it!

<voice_0x01000ABC><se_high>Jessica: Let me know when you've finished, okay?
I'll be waiting here.

<voice_0x01000AB9><se_high>Jessica: Okay then!
Quartermaster, prepare the ship!
<voice_0x01000ABA><se_low>Quartermaster: Aye aye, sir!
<voice_0x01000AB8><se_high>Jessica: Are you ready to set sail?

<voice_0x01000ABB><se_high>Jessica: What, you still aren't ready?
So why are you hanging around here?
Hurry up and do whatever it is you have to do!

<voice_0x01000ABC><se_high>Jessica: I'll be waiting here.
Come back as soon as you're ready.
<voice_0x01000AB0><se_high>Jessica: What? Have you forgotten what happened back at the tower?

<voice_0x01000AB1><se_high>Jessica: Hello!? Dhoulmagus!? Remember!?
And now I hear he's headed south!

<voice_0x01000AB2><se_high>Jessica: We can't follow him so long as the ships are
stuck in port! Now will you take care of that
sea monster?
<voice_0x01000AB3><se_high>Jessica: I knew I could count on you. I still can't get what we saw in the tower out of my mind.
<voice_0x01000AB4><se_high>Jessica: Who is this Dhoulmagus, and what does he want? And why did he murder my brother?

<voice_0x01000AB5><se_high>Jessica: I'll track him to the ends of the earth.
But first, we've got to make the waters safe for ships to sail.

<voice_0x01000AB6><se_high>Jessica: The sea monster that's standing in our way
is supposed to be pretty strong.
You'd better be prepared.

<voice_0x01000AB7><se_high>Jessica: I'll be waiting here.
Come back as soon as you're ready.

<voice_0x01000AC4><se_high>Jessica: Wow, that was really something.
I didn't think he'd be that strong.
<voice_0x01000AC5><se_high>Jessica: But the fact is, he's standing between us and the southern continent. Are you ready to try again?

<voice_0x01000AC6><se_high>Jessica: What, you still aren't ready?
So why are you hanging around here?
Hurry up and do whatever it is you have to do!
